  "id": "BIT-nextcloud-2022-29160",
  "summary": "Sensitive files/data exist after deletion of user account in Nextcloud Android",
  "details": "Nextcloud Android is the Android client for Nextcloud, a self-hosted productivity platform. Prior to version 3.19.0, sensitive tokens, images, and user related details exist after deletion of a user account. This could result in misuse of the former account holder's information. Nextcloud Android version 3.19.0 contains a patch for this issue. There are no known workarounds available.",
